1° @{" Set the 16 colors " link "pal"} with your MWB deamon or other palette utility:
2° Recolor the MWB icon with 3 bitplans wich look trashed on your screen using Iconian, DoIcons...
3° Install my icons using SWAZINFO or any other tool.
